      "body": "In library mode, the Update button calls `onInstall(metadata.id)` even though `onInstall` expects a `MarketplaceEntry`. This causes a type error in TS and a runtime crash in JS when `handleInstall` tries to read `entry.metadata.id`. It only affects the library update path, but it blocks updates entirely. Use the full `entry` (or change the handler signature) to keep the call consistent.",
